,{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"ideal size"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" of its children both dimensions:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["Text(\"A single line of text, too long to fit in a box.\")","    .fixedSize()","    .frame(width: 200, height: 200)","    .border(Color.gray)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This can result in the view exceeding the parent’s bounds, which may or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"may not be the effect you want.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can think of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fixedSize()"},{"type":"text","text":" as the creation of a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"counter proposal"}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to the view size proposed to a view by its parent. The ideal size of a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view, and the specific effects of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fixedSize()"},{"type":"text","text":" depends on the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"particular view and how you have configured it.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To create a view that fixes the view’s size in either the horizontal or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"vertical dimensions, see "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View\/fixedSize(horizontal:vertical:)"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Color"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Color\/fixe